---
import PortalShell from "../layouts/PortalShell.astro";
---

<PortalShell activePage="earn" title="推广合作" description="阿臭弟的小站暂未开放返佣和分销合作。">
  <section class="portal-section affiliate-section">
    <div class="portal-container affiliate-layout">
      <div class="affiliate-intro">
        <p class="section-kicker">Cooperation</p>
        <h1>推广合作</h1>
        <p>阿臭弟的小站目前以微信私域沟通和课程知识库交付为主，暂时不开放返佣、分销或自动推广结算。</p>
        <div class="affiliate-rules">
          <strong>当前状态</strong>
          <span>商业实战Skill以微信沟通确认</span>
          <span>飞书知识库和视频内容人工交付</span>
          <span>返佣与分销功能暂不对外开放</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="affiliate-panel">
        <section class="affiliate-access-form">
          <div>
            <h2>想了解商业实战Skill？</h2>
            <p>请先进入 AI实战库查看具体宝贝。点击立即下单后，会出现微信联系入口；添加时备注想了解的 Skill 名称即可。</p>
          </div>
          <a class="button primary" href="/market/" data-portal-route><i data-lucide="sparkles"></i>进入AI实战库</a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PortalShell>
